div.p:
That the Investments for the Life Policy holders now amount to £1,382,108;
And as evidence of the advantage to Families of Life Assurance,
That the Company has disbursed, among 2943 Claimants, from 1808 to the close of 1851, the sum of £2,476,897, of which a very considerable proportion was for Additions, under the system pursued by this Company.
